  • public class LocationDataMap
extends io.github.zachohara.bukkit.common.persistence.PersistentPlayerData<LocationDataMap.SerializableLocation>
    A LocationDataMap is a PersistentPlayerData map that stores the location of every player when they join or leave the game.
    Author:
    Zach Ohara
